	(1, 5, '成人原味全效牙膏', '九里香', '<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 微软雅黑, arial; font-size: 12px; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.twinlotuschina.com/App/Modules/Index/Tpl/Public/images/sm29.jpg) 0% 5px no-repeat;">双莲全天然植物原味全效牙膏<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">ORIGINAL HERBS<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">十多种珍稀植物研磨全面有效防止口腔问题</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 微软雅黑, arial; font-size: 12px; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.twinlotuschina.com/App/Modules/Index/Tpl/Public/images/sm29.jpg) 0% 5px no-repeat;">针对人群：所有存在牙齿敏感、牙龈出血、牙黄、口气等口腔亚健康问题的人群。</p><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 微软雅黑, arial; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;"><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 微软雅黑, arial; font-size: 12px; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.twinlotuschina.com/App/Modules/Index/Tpl/Public/images/sm29.jpg) 0% 5px no-repeat;">主要功效：<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">能有效防止牙龈出血、口腔溃疡、牙齿过敏；同时可缓解牙周炎、牙肿痛、牙肉萎缩等口腔问题；<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">显著祛除牙菌斑、烟渍、茶渍、咖啡渍等牙渍、牙垢，还原牙齿本色；<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">去除口腔异味，持久保持口气清新。</p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-style: normal; line-height: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', 微软雅黑, arial; font-size: 12px; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background: url(http://www.twinlotuschina.com/App/Modules/Index/Tpl/Public/images/sm29.jpg) 0% 5px no-repeat;">特殊功效：<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">针对牙龈出血、红肿、疼痛症状，将牙膏敷抹患处，获得有效舒缓。<br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">双莲口腔护理品中的明星产品-原味全效牙膏采源于我们泰典秘方的十几种天然植物研磨制成，早期通过药铺渠道提供给口腔患者，随后因应广大消费需求推进大众市场，深受消费者青睐，现为泰国家喻户晓的天然功效牙膏。）</p>', '无香', '成人', '/upload/image/1_1417679034680.png', '￥10.5', '100g', 0, '2014-12-04 15:46:04'),
